{
  "message": "fix: show connection-lost diagnostic text visibly and improve copy feedback (#8659)\n\nThe \"Connection lost\" banner previously hid diagnostic context in a\ntooltip-only title attribute (invisible on touch devices). The restart\ncopy feedback said only \"Copied\" with no context about where to run\nthe command.\n\n- Make diagnostic hint visible as secondary text below the banner\n- Show actual error message (e.g. \"Could not reach agent\") inline\n  when the restart attempt fails\n- Change copy feedback to \"Copied \u2014 run this in your project root\n  terminal\" so users know where to execute the command\n- Add i18n keys for the new strings\n\nFixes #8633\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
